      <code>video-overlay.js</code> file in your app.
    </li>
    <li>
      Add the utility class of <code>video-toggle</code> to your button/trigger.
    </li>
    <li>
      Provide the data- tag <code>data-vid-src</code> generally Dropbox can host
      these video files.
    </li>
    <li>That's it!</li>
  </ol>

